  <li id="comment-33914" class="comment even thread-even depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn"><a href="http://www.emmycooks.com" class="url" rel="ugc external nofollow">emmycooks</a></cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2012/03/this-is-important/#comment-33914"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2012-03-08T09:51:35-05:00">Thursday, March 8, 2012 at 9:51 am</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I love&#8211;love!&#8211;this yeasted waffle recipe and usually make it with part whole wheat flour.  But I completely believe you that buckwheat and maple syrup are a magical combination and I look forward to trying it.  And Margarita, in my experience this batter does make perfectly acceptable pancakes.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
