      <p>exACTLY the recipe I needed today. Thank you. </p>
<p>Congrats on your little one! this is SO exciting!</p>
<p>Margarita- I realize you were not directing your question to me, but I&#39;m taking a stab at it. Mark Bittman suggests making pancakes out of his yeasted waffle batter in How To Make Everything. I&#39;ve always been curious about that myself, but I can&#39;t stop making them in a waffle iron&#8230;they just get so perfectly crisp on the outside. Report back to the comments and let us know how it turns out~</p>
