      <p>I am no stranger to the glory that is buckwheat and maple syrup, (thanks largely to Hemingway&#39;s descriptions in the Nick Adams stories) but this post made me giddy.  GIDDY.  I&#39;m already a devotee of your Waffles of Insane Greatness (which completely live up to their name, and which I  make with spelt flour to great, delicious effect), but I cannot wait to try these.  Thank you and may your little one love them as much as you do.  (Oh, and the eating technique!!!  Love it!!!)</p>
    </div>

