    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Yes, OMG Graeters.</p>
<p>My pop lives in Cincinnati and surprised me with 6 pints delivered to my doorstep in Chicago for Valentine&#39;s Day.  Cute, right?  Not so cute that 4 pints are already gone.</p>
<p>Spring is for fattening up, right?</p>
    </div>

