      <a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-34121' data-commentid="34121" data-postid="427" data-belowelement="comment-34121" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Portland Mom" aria-label='Reply to Portland Mom'>Reply</a>    </div>
