      <p>Yummy &#8211; and CONGRATS on making it through the first trimester!  </p>
<p>This is going to be so crazy awesome, because a. you are having a baby, and b. I am having a baby, too (am due 9/24). So we can go through all the crazy cravings together, right?!  (Speaking of which, those waffles look amazing).  I&#39;m glad I&#39;m not the only one who has been craving what I&#39;ve dubbed a &#8220;5-year-old&#39;s diet&#8221; of starch, starch, and more starch (I just made your lemon-ginger Scottish scones this weekend and felt all fancy because they actually had flavor!).  </p>
<p>So.  CONGRATS again &#8211; and have fun!!!  Isn&#39;t it crazy to think that everytime you enter a room, there are actually <i>two</i> people entering that room?</p>
